eNCA's Ace sports reporter Hloni Mtimkulu JOHANNESBURG - eNCA's Ace sports reporter Hloni Mtimkulu has been honoured for her sterling work in journalism. She was recognised with the chairperson's award at a glitzy ceremony on Friday night. The prestigious Futballing Girls Gauteng Women Sports awards, held annually, celebrate outstanding achievements in the women's sport, and Hloni Mtimkulu has been at the forefront of reporting on that.